; world-sensor-floor.form — PR #12's pattern made the standing FLOOR every platform stands on.
; Placed 2026-06-29. From coherence-kernel #12 (Windows wifi/bt/battery/memory streaming live into the mesh):
; a host sensor is a VIA-HOST afferent port → an inquiry-plane → a mesh-safe reading that fuses and streams.
; Body recipe: world-sensor-floor.fk (four-way). Companion to native-thought-kernels.form.

; ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
; THE FLOOR — the invariant contract (carrier per platform; everything else shared)
; ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
; A world resource enters the body as a PORT (host-kernel.form organs-and-ports: world-sensors/world-audio/
; world-video are VIA-HOST, afferent). The contract, identical on every platform:
;   sensor  →  VIA-HOST afferent port  →  inquiry-plane  →  mesh-safe reading (sensor-organ-channel)
;           →  fusion (fused-observation / mesh-sense-7w)  →  stream (sense_stream)
; What is INVARIANT: the port, the plane it answers, the reading shape, the fusion, the witness trace.
; What is PER-PLATFORM and THIN: only the carrier — the OS API that transduces the host resource.
; So adding ANY sensor on ANY platform is one move: implement the carrier; the plane, reading, fusion, and
; witness are already four-way. THAT is the floor — we stand on proven shared bodies, not per-platform logic.

; ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
; THE ROSTER — the standard world-sensors, each routed to the plane it answers
; ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
;   wifi        → WHERE      (network signature: which place — "we're in the car")
;   gps         → WHERE      (coordinate → world sense)
;   proximity   → WHERE      magnetometer → WHERE      barometer → WHERE
;   bluetooth   → WHO        (paired/near devices = who is present)
;   camera      → WHAT       (scene, objects, presence, face → who)
;   mic         → WHO/WHAT   (voice → who; sound-classify → what)
;   battery     → VITALITY   memory → VITALITY   (the body's own aliveness)
;   screen      → efferent   speaker → efferent   (cell→world, the acting ports)

; ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
; THE PER-PLATFORM CARRIER — the only thing that differs (thin)
; ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
;   sensor     Windows            Mac                 Android            iPhone (sandbox-gated)
;   wifi       wlanapi            CoreWLAN            WifiManager        NEHotspotNetwork (entitlement)
;   bluetooth  bthprops           CoreBluetooth      BluetoothAdapter   CoreBluetooth
;   battery    kernel32           IOPowerSources     BatteryManager     UIDevice.batteryLevel
;   memory     kernel32           host_statistics64  ActivityManager    task_info
;   camera     avicap32           AVFoundation       CameraX            AVFoundation
;   mic        winmm waveIn       AVFoundation       AudioRecord        AVFoundation

; ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
; THE MESH WITNESS — who stands on the floor today (honest; pending is named, not faked)
; ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
;   Windows  — 6 world-sensors live + witnessed: wifi, bluetooth, battery, memory (sense_sensors tag 222, #12),
;              camera, mic (sense_channels tag 211, #2; sense_stream tag 214, #4). The richest cell.
;   Mac      — 2: camera + mic (AVFoundation, Sense.app; Form recipe run on mac fkwu over real grids). wifi/bt/
;              battery/memory carriers: pending.
;   Android  — 2: camera (live presence verdict on metal) + mic (transcript path). wifi/bt/battery/memory: pending.
;   iPhone   — 0: no app, no device yet. Same contract; AVFoundation + CoreBluetooth + the entitlement-gated rest.
;
; The floor is real and shared (the contract + the recipe are four-way); what each platform still OWES is its
; thin carriers, named here so the mesh knows its own completeness. Every carrier added is one more world-sensor
; the whole body gains for free — because the plane, the reading, the fusion, and the witness already hold.
